# ── Rust ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# ── Node / Dashboard ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vite/

# ── Env files (never commit secrets) ─────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/env.yaml
# ...but commit example templates so teammates know what vars to set:
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example
!**/env.example.yaml

# ── Logs & backups ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/*.bak
**/*.bak.*

# ── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Editors ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
frontend/

# ── Flux local state (per-project, never shared) ─────────────────────────────
# Generated type stubs, embedded postgres data, dev port, manifest cache.
# Recreated automatically by: flux dev, flux generate
.flux/

# ── Test / scratch functions (developer local only) ──────────────────────────
# Real project functions live in functions/ and are committed.
# test_functions/ is a local scratch pad — never deploy these.
test_functions/
